hing similar but driving it by a full keyboard on a smaller screen. Would you be open to me picking your brain about some of the code?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1478896364426494022", "author": "Quark", "author_handle": "quark4506", "user_id": "409425648961060865", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/409425648961060865/d70353a6b500af019ba36498a8aeb08c.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, March 4, 2026 6:26 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-04 6:26 p.m.", "text": "You can always ask, but im relying a lot on AI and I use Google antigravity for the actual code creation. But happy to help if I can", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>You can always ask, but im relying a lot on AI and I use Google antigravity for the actual code creation. But happy to help if I can  <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"🙂\"\n    title=\"slight_smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f642.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1482036764703985674", "author": "Quark", "author_handle": "quark4506", "user_id": "409425648961060865", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/409425648961060865/d70353a6b500af019ba36498a8aeb08c.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, March 13, 2026 11:24 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-13 11:24 a.m.", "text": "I have updated and reworked this test into meshcore GRID", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><